            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "市區半新樓2房連平台6球推拍 樓價7年蒸發44% 貶值510萬元",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">樓市交投轉旺，拍賣場又見低價筍盤。樓齡7年的大角咀<a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"利奧坊‧凱岸\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:利奧坊‧凱岸;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://b.28hse.com/47PwvK6\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">利奧坊‧凱岸</a>一個2房連平台特色戶，屬市區罕有放盤，銀主將於下周二（4月14日）假環亞物業拍賣行以660萬元推拍，料將吸引用家及投資者爭購。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"720\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/5BKRDq9gh_hewtIHADNSAg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTcyMA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/28hse_com_210/d210ca553c521360c9931e81b635cb8b\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">更多消息：</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"旺角劏舖搶高6倍至70萬沽 每月收租4,000元 業主持貨14年仍蝕77%\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:旺角劏舖搶高6倍至70萬沽 每月收租4,000元 業主持貨14年仍蝕77%;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://b.28hse.com/4twdJzH\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">旺角劏舖搶高6倍至70萬沽 每月收租4,000元 業主持貨14年仍蝕77%</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"德福五屍命案單位流拍 「凶宅大王」未舉手已敗陣：「出師未捷身未死」 「鬼王」潘紹聰稱單位「安全、舒服、有人氣」\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:德福五屍命案單位流拍 「凶宅大王」未舉手已敗陣：「出師未捷身未死」 「鬼王」潘紹聰稱單位「安全、舒服、有人氣」;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://b.28hse.com/47P77nJ\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">德福五屍命案單位流拍 「凶宅大王」未舉手已敗陣：「出師未捷身未死」 「鬼王」潘紹聰稱單位「安全、舒服、有人氣」</a></p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"720\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/JYrOOwuz8mMgkJrHcw1Y.g--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTcyMA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/28hse_com_210/fba971123ecb94fa9a81d814aeaadc6c\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">上述單位為利奧坊‧凱岸2座低層連平台單位，實用面積379平方呎，採2房間隔，連144平方呎平台，將於下周二以660萬元開拍，折合呎價僅約17,414元。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-7a86a1b9-f3e9-3c6c-905f-011ce42d0ec6-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"720\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/0B7Mvy2OcvXPmckjvtPnlQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTcyMA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/28hse_com_210/0a2c27c005becbdfbf6559398746a478\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">從放盤相可見，單位內籠新淨，採開放式廚房，玄關及客廳訂造大型儲物櫃。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"720\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/J7EWzbZ3RZeBJQvxTqFgKw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTcyMA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/28hse_com_210/fffba15c2246769a983fc57e08ea3b17\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">靠近客廳的細房設有閣樓及衣櫃，主人房訂造地台床及置物架。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"720\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/_9vCxMqjSBmLjWJk729ZdQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTcyMA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/28hse_com_210/1b85f775d781e7fa87766bb1722c764b\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">衛生間有窗可通風。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"720\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Un..bJ5sx3K0Ev4ixRi2qw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTcyMA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/28hse_com_210/977bd4c818ac2470647bb60d940b14ba\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">單位將於明日（4月9日）開放參觀。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"720\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/7GN5fGSlpOq5hxVTqknS1A--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTcyMA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/28hse_com_210/f9df5575a97cb85a668abb605191cd0c\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據悉，原業主於2019年11月以1,170.05萬元購入單位，其後斷供淪為銀主盤，早前曾3度流拍，今次開價與之前3次相若，較約7年前買入價低510.05萬元或44%，較銀行估價739萬元亦低約11%。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"720\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/CLjHG0OhMQw9_F0YE0cRxw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTcyMA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/28hse_com_210/d0477b4475ca9ec6230a714ae5dffec6\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">根據28Hse網站資料，利奧坊‧凱岸近期平均成交呎價約18,774 元，較上述單位開拍呎價高1,360元或7.8%。屋苑目前共<a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"17個放盤\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:17個放盤;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://b.28hse.com/4ttL7qJ\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">17個放盤</a>，涵蓋開放式至1房，叫價由370萬元至551萬元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">延伸閱讀: <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"大角咀\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:大角咀;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.28hse.com/estate/detail/大角咀-27379\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">大角咀</a>     <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"旺角\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:旺角;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.28hse.com/estate/detail/旺角-27383\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">旺角</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">延伸閱讀:</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">* <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"新聞連結\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:新聞連結;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.28hse.com/news/%E5%B8%82%E5%8D%80%E5%8D%8A%E6%96%B0%E6%A8%932%E6%88%BF%E9%80%A3%E5%B9%B3%E5%8F%B06%E7%90%83%E6%8E%A8%E6%8B%8D-%E6%A8%93%E5%83%B97%E5%B9%B4%E8%92%B8%E7%99%